						</div>
						<div class="space-y-2">
							<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white uppercase tracking-wider">02. Log & Track</h3>
							<p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-gray-400">Record expenses with one click. Toggle payment status to know exactly what's paid and what's pending.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="relative z-10 bg-white dark:bg-slate-950 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 text-center space-y-6">
