						</div>
						<div class="space-y-2">
							<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white uppercase tracking-wider">03. Review</h3>
							<p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-gray-400">Navigate months to review past spending or plan ahead. Let recurring costs handle themselves automatically.</p>
